metadata.name: Leaves of Change: Presence
metadata.description:
For a background on this collection, please read the collection description. This NFT piece is a full and clear profile of our beloved Evie. If you focus on her right ear you can see it has transformed into leaves, olives, and oranges.

When Evie passed away in November of 2019, we were living in Turkey for a year. We buried her in a family field of olive and orange groves.
